fields.name: Domain of Sanction
fields.description: A divine sword forged with the authority of judgment. Its radiant blade channels raw energy to strike down foes with unmatched precision, embodying both elegance and destructive power. Perfect for those who seek dominance on the battlefield.

fields.name: Domain of Genesis
fields.description: Channel the power of Finality with Domain of Genesis—dual pistols forged from the essence of Fire and Time. Their active unleashes a blazing barrage, leaving foes aflame and unable to resist, while stance transitions reward mastery.

fields.name: Domain of Incandescence
fields.description: Master the inferno. These blazing pistols summon a fiery tempest upon the battlefield, blasting enemies into cinders before erupting in a final, cataclysmic burst.

fields.name: Domain of the Void
fields.description: A cosmic weapon forged in the Foundry, these dual pistols harness the Herrscher of the Void’s powers. Each implosion shatters reality—tearing foes apart, restoring Herrscher Charge, and crushing shields with spatial devastation.

fields.name: Tranquil Rhapsody
fields.description: Step into Nightwalk—vanish from sight, then unleash a devastating shadow leap that freezes enemies in your wake. A true dominator of darkness.

fields.name: Echo of Paradise: Time Ruins
fields.description: These crimson flintlocks crack with the power of time itself, striking foes with electrifying resonance—and igniting your team's synergy in a blaze of lightning.

fields.name: Frozen Naraka
fields.description: This frost-encased blade surrounds you with a chilling aura of invulnerability and slows all who dare approach—then delivers a devastating final strike to freeze and finish them.

fields.name: Domain of Unity
fields.description: “Empty your heart; let your blade bind all as one.” Each electrifying slash shields you in lightning—then fractures time itself, freezing enemies as you stand unbreakable at the heart of the storm.

fields.name: Star Destroyer 19C-X
fields.description: “Unleash the wrath of cold malice across the battlefield.” Charge into barrage mode and rain down a hail of homing missiles. Each salvo shatters defenses, intensifies your resolve, and tears enemies apart with mounting fury.

fields.name: Falcon Flare: FINAL
fields.description: “Let frozen fury take flight and consume all.” Unleash a chilling barrage that warps space with each shot. Ignite icy implosions, shatter barriers, and bind your foes in the cold breath of annihilation.

fields.name: Tower of the Past: Silk Ladder
fields.description: “From the ruins of Babel rises a fragile thread—woven with defiance.” Lock enemies in place as you unleash fiery cluster bombs and devastating bursts. Pierce through chaos, slow their resolve, and let your inferno bind and burn them where they stand.

fields.name: Hekate's Sombre
fields.description: “Dark blades rain from the abyss—obliterate all beneath the twilight.” Unleash a celestial storm of blades that devastate your foes, while summoning an ethereal cross that becomes the harbinger of relentless physical carnage.

fields.name: Basilisk's Image: Deathshroud
fields.description: “From the serpent’s shadow, time itself coils in your command.” Summon a serpent domain that ensnares your foes—marked prey fall to crackling combo strikes, lightning surges, and frozen resolve.

fields.name: Shuhadaku of Uriel
fields.description: “When the heavens burn, only void remains.” Wield the inferno of divine destruction—each charged slash sears through reality, igniting your foes while life slips away, and transforming pain into apocalyptic power.

fields.name: Surtr Muspellsverd
fields.description: “Wield the flame of gods—as Ragnarok unfolds, Asgard burns in its wake.” Sacrifice your lifeforce to summon blazing fury: ignite enemies, forge a protective shield, and unleash relentless firepower that scorches both enemy and destiny.

fields.name: Labor of Olympus
fields.description: “Wield the trial of gods—harness celestial wrath at the cost of mortal will.” This experimental blade absorbs ambient Honkai energy, unlocking blazing power: during Burst or after Ultimates, every strike burns foes with divine fire.

fields.name: Cosmic Duality
fields.description: “Balance the cosmic scales—heal, heal again, and empower your allies through the echoes of Yin and Yang.” These gauntlets restore health and SP with each pulse, while weaving elemental synergy—ignite your power, then ignite your team’s potential.

fields.name: Iris of Helheim
fields.description: “Channel the mourning mist—resurrect power from death itself.” Unleash soul-draining haze that elevates Fallen Rosemary’s might. Summon runes, pause time, and bathe enemies in electrifying sorrow.

fields.name: Sanguine Gaze: Union
fields.description: “When you gaze into the abyss, the abyss returns the stare—united, they consume.” Harness the abyssal pull of chain claws: drag enemies to you or rush to them with lethal slashes that restore your Carmine Gash and weave into your final strike.

fields.name: Lance of Longinus
fields.description: A sacred spear crafted from the Tree of Life. Its thrust births celestial control—forcing foes into helpless submission and unleashing coordinated counter-strikes that cleave through shields and ignite divine retribution.

fields.name: Abyss Flower: Liminal Spiral
fields.description: “Where creation and destruction entwine, the divine lance blooms”—each strike balances healing and devastation through the spiral of fate.

fields.name: Mitternachts Waltz
fields.description: Strike true with lightning-tipped arrows. Each hit ignites swirling energy that empowers your team’s elemental skills and fuels your relentless rhythm of attacks.

fields.name: Purana Phantasma: Nighteye
fields.description: Awaken the frost—let spectral crystals bind the battlefield in icy dominance, with the silent grace of a hunting cat

fields.name: Lost Conviction: Damnation
fields.description: Four lightning butterflies circle the wielder, striking enemies with relentless precision. Each surge amplifies your control of the battlefield, binding power and punishment as one.
